# iptables-cpp
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).


## [0.3.0] - 2020-07-19
### Added
- IpTablesHandler.cpp
- IpTablesHandlerTest.cpp

### Changed
- Replaced libiptc implementation with iptables-store file implementation
  See Removed section for more details
- Renamed IpTablesWrapper.cpp to IptcWrapper.cpp

### Removed
- Depreciated IptcWrapper.cpp
  libiptc is not intended as an external API, netfilter devs recommend using system() calls or iptables-restore

## [0.2.0] - 2020-07-18
### Added 
- Address.cpp
- Chain.cpp
- ChainMap.cpp
- IpTablesWrapper.cpp
- Rule.cpp
- RuleMap.cpp
- main.cpp
- AddressTest.cpp
- ChainMapTest.cpp
- ChainTest.cpp
- IpTablesWrapperTest.cpp
- MainTest.cpp
- RuleMapTest.cpp
- RuleTest.cpp
- Generic API structure
- Linking to libiptc headers
- Information in README.md
- CMake build
- Build script
- Dockerfile
- VS code configuration, launch, settings, and task files

## [0.1.0] - 2020-07-14
### Added
- Initial commit

